'''Colli del Tronto''' is a ''[[comune]]'' (municipality) in the [[Province of Ascoli Piceno]] in the [[Italy|Italian]] region [[Marche]], located about 80 km south of [[Ancona]] and about 14 km northeast of [[Ascoli Piceno]]. As of [[31 December]] [[2004]], it had a population of 3,290 and an area of 5.9 km<U+00B2>.<ref name="istat">All demographics and other statistics: Italian statistical institute [[Istat]].</ref>

Colli del Tronto borders the following municipalities: [[Ancarano]], [[Ascoli Piceno]], [[Castorano]], [[Spinetoli]].


